ActCanada Mortgage and Housing Corporation Act
PrecisApproval of the reappointment by the Minister of Employment and Social Development of BRIAN K. JOHNSTON of Toronto, Ontario, as a director of the Board of Directors of Canada Mortgage and Housing Corporation, to hold office during pleasure, on a part-time basis, for a term of three years.
